data.description: Welcome Home! This lovely half-brick exterior home is located on a nice-sized corner lot. As you pull up to the home you will notice the well-manicured lot with tons of curb appeal and a large driveway. Continue inside you will notice the bright and airy sitting room that allows an enormous amount of natural light in daily.  Off to your left under the beautiful archway is the living room which continues to show all the natural light surrounding this home. Straight back through the living room is the family room which is cozy and perfect for those movie nights! Across the hall is the dining room with a gorgeous chandelier. The dining room also features a built-in window seat. The spacious kitchen features tons of counter and cabinet space, stainless steel stove, stainless steel dishwasher, and a double-sided basin sink. The french doors off the kitchen lead out onto the screened porch that makes for your own private oasis to relax and unwind. Back inside and up the steps features 3 spacious bedrooms with ample closet space to suit your needs. The upper floor features 3 bedrooms and a full bathroom with a claw foot tub. The finished basement leaves you with tons of opportunities for a playroom, additional family room, home office, or more! The home is located to convenient shopping and transportation. Schedule your showing today you do not want to miss this! *This home is being sold as is*
